name: stress¹
description:
This series of art, called «stress», is about the formation and development of stress in a person's life. Each artwork is a part of my personal experience. I hope in this you will find feelings, similar to your own worries. 

"Anxiety. Strengthen your grip".
 
The first encounter with stress. You feel uncomfortable, but don't kid yourself, a bit longer and you will be swallowed up by a flood of worry and anxiety, alternating between peace and oppression.
